   CODE NAME         : target26.sas
   DESCRIPTION       : Reference SAS program for target 4
   SOFTWARE/VERSION# : SAS V9
   INPUT             : http://phuse-scripts.googlecode.com/svn/trunk/scriptathon2014/data/advs.xpt
